content.title: RHBA-2025:0304: .NET 8.0 bug fix and enhancement update (Important)
content.description:
.NET Core is a managed-software framework. It implements a subset of the .NET
framework APIs and several new APIs, and it includes a CLR implementation.

Bug Fix(es) and Enhancement(s):

* Update .NET 8.0 to SDK 8.0.112 and Runtime 8.0.12 [rhel-9.5.z] (RHEL-71556)Bug Fix(es) and Enhancement(s):
